data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom plus den or office, 2 full bath, lake view single family home in Fort Myers gated neighborhood. Interior property features include open living room kitchen area, split floor plans, granite counters and ample closet, cabinet and storage throughout the home. Located on a private corner lot, the home also features an expansive backyard, with beautiful lake views from a private screened in patio/lanai. Lindsford neighborhood has so many amazing resort style amenities, including lagoon pool, fishing pier, gym, media and social rooms, as well as tennis, basketball and bocce courts. All centrally located within close proximity to all of SWFL major business and recreational areas including downtown, airports, beaches, spring-training venues, hospitals and shopping malls, as well as a quick access (5 to 10 minute drive) to Interstate I75.
